
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>GPT Lab - AI Learning Hub</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f8fbfd;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --muted: #64748b;
      --line: #e2e8f0;
      --soft-line: #eef2f7;
      --blue: #0f6fb7;
      --blue-soft: #eff9ff;
      --green: #0e9f6e;
      --green-soft: #ecfdf7;
      --yellow: #fff1a5;
      --shadow: 0 12px 18px rgba(15, 23, 41, 0.06);
      --radius: 12px;
      --content: 1088px;
      color-scheme: light;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: "Noto Sans TC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "PingFang TC", Arial, sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    button,
    input {
      font: inherit;
    }

    button {
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0 auto 0 0;
      z-index: 40;
      width: 205px;
      background: #fff;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 25px 18px 32px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .brand {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 42px 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      margin: 0 0 34px 5px;
    }

    .mark,
    .mini-mark {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .brand-title {
      display: block;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .brand-subtitle {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 3px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .nav {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .nav a {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 38px;
      padding: 0 18px 0 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #334155;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav a:hover {
      transform: translateX(2px);
      color: var(--blue);
    }

    .nav a.active {
      background: var(--blue-soft);
      color: var(--blue);
    }

    .learning-note {
      margin-top: auto;
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid #d3f8e9;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--green-soft);
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .learning-note strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .learning-note p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin-left: 205px;
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 30;
      display: flex;
      gap: 26px;
      align-items: center;
      width: min(var(--content), calc(100vw - 288px));
      min-height: 68px;
      margin-left: 43px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      padding: 11px 31px;
    }

    .mobile-menu {
      display: none;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .search {
      position: relative;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .search span {
      position: absolute;
      left: 15px;
      top: 50%;
      color: var(--muted);
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      font-size: 16px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .search input {
      width: 100%;
      height: 44px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 0 16px 0 40px;
      outline: none;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .search input:focus {
      border-color: #93c5fd;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(15, 111, 183, 0.1);
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 44px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 0 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(15, 23, 41, 0.08);
    }

    .btn.primary {
      border-color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--ink);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn.compact {
      min-height: 36px;
      padding: 0 14px;
      border-radius: 9px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .content {
      width: min(var(--content), calc(100vw - 288px));
      margin-left: 43px;
      padding: 32px 0 72px;
    }

    section {
      scroll-margin-top: 96px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 700px) 364px;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: stretch;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .hero-card,
    .panel,
    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-card {
      min-height: 470px;
      padding: 34px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: fit-content;
      min-height: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--green-soft);
      color: var(--green);
      padding: 0 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .pill.blue {
      background: var(--blue-soft);
      color: var(--blue);
    }

    .hero-card h1 {
      margin: 26px 0 24px;
      font-size: 64px;
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .hero-card h2 {
      margin: 0 0 28px;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 26px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .hero-card p {
      max-width: 610px;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: auto;
      padding-top: 34px;
    }

    .side-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 26px;
    }

    .info-card {
      min-height: 222px;
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .card-head {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 42px 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .mini-mark {
      background: var(--green-soft);
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .mini-mark.blue {
      background: var(--blue-soft);
      color: var(--blue);
    }

    .card-head strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .card-head span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 7px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .info-card h3,
    .quick-panel h3,
    .prompt-card h3,
    .workflow-card h3,
    .guide-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .info-card p,
    .quick-panel p,
    .prompt-card p,
    .workflow-card p,
    .guide-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .info-card p {
      margin: 16px 0 0;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .quick-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 76px;
    }

    .quick-panel {
      padding: 22px;
      min-height: 260px;
    }

    .quick-panel p {
      margin: 10px 0 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .quick-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .quick-list button {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 42px;
      border: 1px solid var(--soft-line);
      border-radius: 9px;
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 10px 14px;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.35;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .quick-list button:hover {
      border-color: #bae6fd;
      background: #f1fbff;
      transform: translateX(2px);
    }

    .section-heading {
      max-width: 920px;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .section-heading h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .section-heading p {
      margin: 22px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .course-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 32px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 92px;
    }

    .course-card {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 340px;
      flex-direction: column;
      background: var(--yellow);
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .course-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .course-card h3 {
      margin: 30px 0 18px;
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .course-card p {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .checks {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 0 0 22px;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .checks li {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 14px 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: start;
      color: #334155;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .checks li::before {
      content: "";
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      margin-top: 2px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--green);
    }

    .course-card .btn {
      margin-top: auto;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .filter-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin: -10px 0 30px;
    }

    .filter {
      min-width: 96px;
      min-height: 30px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 0 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .filter.active,
    .filter:hover {
      border-color: var(--blue);
      background: var(--blue);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .result-line {
      min-height: 22px;
      margin: -18px 0 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .prompt-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 92px;
    }

    .prompt-card {
      min-height: 320px;
      padding: 20px 22px 22px;
    }

    .prompt-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .prompt-card h3 {
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 19px;
    }

    .prompt-card > p {
      margin: 14px 0 28px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .prompt-box {
      min-height: 144px;
      border: 1px solid var(--soft-line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: #334155;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
    }

    .workflow-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 92px;
    }

    .workflow-card {
      min-height: 420px;
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .workflow-card .card-head {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .workflow-card > p {
      margin: 0 0 28px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .steps {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .step {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 34px 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: start;
      padding: 0;
      border: 0;
      background: transparent;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .step-number {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 9px;
      background: var(--blue-soft);
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .step strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .step span:last-child {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .step:hover .step-number,
    .step.active .step-number {
      background: var(--blue);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .guide-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 92px;
    }

    .guide-card {
      min-height: 230px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .guide-card h3 {
      margin: 22px 0 14px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .guide-card p {
      min-height: 48px;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .guide-card .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .faq-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 20px;
      max-width: 816px;
      margin: 0 auto 44px;
    }

    .faq-item {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .faq-item summary {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      min-height: 72px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
      display: none;
    }

    .faq-item summary::after {
      content: "+";
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .faq-item[open] summary::after {
      content: "-";
    }

    .faq-item p {
      margin: -12px 20px 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .footer {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .toast {
      position: fixed;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: 24px;
      z-index: 80;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--ink);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22);
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transform: translate(-50%, 16px);
      transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .toast.show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translate(-50%, 0);
    }

    .modal-backdrop {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 70;
      display: none;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.38);
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .modal-backdrop.show {
      display: flex;
    }

    .modal {
      width: min(640px, 100%);
      max-height: min(760px, calc(100vh - 40px));
      overflow: auto;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.24);
    }

    .modal-head {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px 22px;
    }

    .modal-head h2 {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .modal-close {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .modal-body {
      padding: 22px;
      color: #334155;
    }

    .modal-body p {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .modal-body ul {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .modal-body li {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .empty {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      display: none;
      border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .is-hidden {
      display: none !important;
    }

    .flash {
      animation: flash 1.1s ease;
    }

    @keyframes flash {
      0%, 100% {
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }
      25%, 70% {
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(15, 111, 183, 0.18), var(--shadow);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1180px) {
      :root {
        --content: calc(100vw - 48px);
      }

      .sidebar {
        transform: translateX(-100%);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      }

      .sidebar.open {
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      .page {
        margin-left: 0;
      }

      .topbar,
      .content {
        width: min(100% - 32px, 1088px);
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }

      .mobile-menu {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .side-stack {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .course-grid,
      .workflow-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .guide-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .topbar {
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 11px 12px;
      }

      .topbar .btn {
        display: none;
      }

      .content {
        padding-top: 20px;
      }

      .hero-card {
        min-height: 420px;
        padding: 28px 22px;
      }

      .hero-card h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
      }

      .hero-card h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .hero-card p {
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .quick-row,
      .side-stack,
      .course-grid,
      .prompt-grid,
      .workflow-grid,
      .guide-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .section-heading {
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .section-heading h2 {
        font-size: 26px;
      }

      .course-card,
      .prompt-card,
      .workflow-card,
      .guide-card {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .prompt-top {
        align-items: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <aside class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
    <a class="brand" href="#home" aria-label="GPT Lab Home">
      <span class="mark">GPT</span>
      <span>
        <span class="brand-title">GPT Lab</span>
        <span class="brand-subtitle">AI Learning Hub</span>
      </span>
    </a>
    <nav class="nav" aria-label="Primary">
      <a class="active" href="#home">Home</a>
      <a href="#courses">Courses</a>
      <a href="#prompts">Prompt Library</a>
      <a href="#workflow">Workflow</a>
      <a href="#guide">Quick Guide</a>
      <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="learning-note">
      <strong>學習路線</strong>
      <p>從基礎概念開始，接著練習 Prompt、Custom GPT 與可重複的 AI 工作流。</p>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <main class="page">
    <header class="topbar">
      <button class="mobile-menu" type="button" id="menuButton" aria-label="開啟選單">☰</button>
      <label class="search" for="siteSearch">
